tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE survey_data 
(
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_id INT NOT NULL,
    survey_date DATE,
    survey_responses JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyResponses (
  response_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_id UUID,
  survey_id UUID,
  question_id UUID,
  answer TEXT,
  response_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE SurveyQuestions (
  question_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_id UUID,
  question_text TEXT,
  is_required BOOLEAN,
  question_type TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE survey_participants (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  email VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE survey_questions (
  question_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  question_text TEXT,
  category VARCHAR(50),
  difficulty_level VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id INT,
  question_id INT,
  response TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE SurveyParticipants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  email VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyResponses (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id INT,
  question_id INT,
  response_text TEXT,
  response_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    respondent_id INT,
    response_value TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE survey_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    respondent_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    response_value TEXT
);
